remarks.para: This structure supersedes the IMAGEHLP_DUPLICATE_SYMBOL structure. For more information, see Updated Platform Support. IMAGEHLP_DUPLICATE_SYMBOL is defined as follows in DbgHelp.h.

summary.para: The size of the structure, in bytes. The caller must set this member to sizeof(IMAGEHLP_DUPLICATE_SYMBOL64).
A pointer to an array of symbols ( structures). The number of entries in the array is specified by the NumberOfDups member.
The index into the symbol array for the selected symbol.
